paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted information on BRCA2 variants, including penetrance data and clinical significance.

functional_data.summary: BRCA2 exons 10 and 11 are classified as coldspots with no pathogenic variants.

variants.additional_notes: Exons 10 and 11 of BRCA2 account for ~65% of the coding sequence and have no pathogenic variants.
key_quotes: BRCA2 exons 10 and 11, which account for ~65% of the coding sequence, have no putative P+LP missense variants (0.0%), but contain 62.1% (110/177) of B+LB variation.
